description:
This market refers to the NHL Regular Season Matchup between the Seattle Kraken and the St. Louis Blues scheduled for October 8. 2024, 4:30 PM ET.

If the Seattle Kraken win, the market will resolve to “Kraken”.

If the St. Louis Blues win, the market will resolve to “Blues”.

This market will resolve based on the winner of the game, which includes regular time, overtime, and penalties. If the game is cancelled or postponed past 11:59 PM ET on October 15, 2024, this market will resolve to 50-50.

The primary resolution source for this market will be official information from National Hockey League (NHL.com), however, a consensus of credible reporting may also be used.
